Section: libs

Package: libcutiedatetime
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cutie Shell date/time settings library
 Shared library providing the CutieDateTime C++ backend used by
 cutie-settings to configure the system clock, timezone, and NTP.

Package: libcutiedatetime-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: libcutiedatetime (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cutie Shell date/time settings library — development files
 Headers and pkg-config file for building against libcutiedatetime.

Package: qml6-module-cutiedatetime
Architecture: any
Depends: libcutiedatetime (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Cutie Shell date/time QML plugin
 QML plugin that exposes CutieDateTime as a singleton importable via
 "import Cutie.Datetime" in QML files.
